CO2 intensity of electricity.source: Calculated using Cambium's aer_co2_load_c metric, which is the average emissions rate of the generation that is allocated to a region's end-use load, inclusive of the effects of imported and exported power. Bi-annual hourly data at the ReEDS BA region are first mapped to EMM regions and then averaged across each year; then these data are interpolated and converted to Mt CO2/TWh.

End-use electricity price.source: Calculated using converter.py, from Table 54, 'End-use Prices' for each building sector and EMM region, from the 2023 EIA Annual Energy Outlook (2022-2050); previous years (2016-2021) backfilled based on 2022 value from AEO 2023
